Corps of Engineers Specification CRD C-572-74.
The temperature control can be adjusted from
250-500º Fahrenheit. BoMetals thermoplasatic
irons are constructed of the highest quality
components. A detailed Waterstop Field Splicing
Guide is available upon request.
short_description:
100% factory tested, adjustable temperature,
heavy duty vinyl grip, teflon peel and stick
cover, standard 110-120 VAC/8 Amp, 8’ power
cord, UL Listed.
